## Business Model Basics

### Revenue
| Stream | Model |
|--------|-------|
| Monthly service | Subscription ($20-50/line) |
| Device sales | Phone/accessory markup |
| Add-on services | International, hotspot, etc. |

### Cost Structure
| Cost | Approximate |
|------|-------------|
| Wholesale data/voice | $15-30/line |
| SIM/provisioning | $2-5/line |
| Billing platform | $1-3/line |
| Customer support | $3-5/line |
| Customer acquisition | $100-200/customer |

### Margin Reality
- Gross margin: 20-40%
- After support/acquisition: Often negative Y1-2
- Scale required for profitability

