## Alternative Ideas

*If mobile service is appealing but MVNO is too heavy:*

### Affiliate/Referral
- Partner with existing MVNO
- Earn referral fees
- No operational burden

### App Layer Only
- Build app that works on any carrier
- Focus on software differentiation
- Avoid telecom complexity

### Reseller Tier
- Some MVNOs have reseller programs
- Lower barrier than full MVNO
- Limited customization

